data.description:
Cul-de-sac charmer in the Eagle Landing golf community. A bright open floor plan that features extra tall ceilings, the main kitchen and living area is expansive with multiple setup options. You'll find plenty of kitchen storage with 42'' cabinets, walk-in pantry and quartz countertops with breakfast bar. Spacious downstairs master bedroom with separate tub/shower en-suite bathroom also has a large walk-in closet. Separate formal dining/flex space AND office space big enough it can be converted into another bedroom. Perfect for visitors that don't like stairs! Upstairs you'll find 3 large bedrooms and bathroom with dual vanity. 
From the recently refinished hand-scraped bamboo flooring, deep front porch, wooded backyard view, to the large driveway (parks 6 cars easily)
